flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|application_1|1|Start by making the work discussable|Start by putting the task into words for another person. Name the question, explain the current state, and ask for the kind of response that would help.|social_exchange|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::application_1
